post_title: JETA1 FOR SALE IN ROTTERDAM
post_text:
Dear sir / madam,

Our company is in direct contact with a reliable seller who is
currently having JETA1 for sale in Port of Rotterdam to reliable
and serious Buyers only. Below is our procedure and if interested
please revert back without delays as it on a first come first
serve basis.

CI DIP AND PAY FOB ROTTERDAM NON-NEGOTIABLE
1. BUYER issues ICPO after receiving SCO.
2. SELLER issue CI.
3. BUYER Signs and returns Commercial Invoice to the SELLER.
4. SELLER issues to the BUYER below documents:
A. Tank Storage Reeceipt
B. Fresh SGS Q and Q report done in Rotterdam certifying the
quantity and quality in Shore tank
C. Irrevocable Commitment Letter to Supplier,
5. BUYER extends seller tanks for 7-10 days.
6. SELLER releases to the BUYER DTA in order to conduct dip test
in SELLER' S leased tank.
7. BUYER proceeds with Dip test in his tank with SGS official and
Receive Fresh SGS Report not less than 24 Hours alongside ASTC.
(Authorization to Sell and Collect the product).
8. SELLER Change title of the product in BUYER's name and BUYER
pays for total cost of product and seller pays commissions, via
MT 103


Best Regards,
